title: Global Beauty Masters - Season 1 Complete
description:
GLOBAL BEAUTY MASTERS is a Television series about the most extreme hair, makeup, nails and fashion competition of all time. It is the "World Cup of Beauty".

The television series is based on the live event Battle of the Strands, featuring top salon teams from the U.S. and around the globe to step it up in their final battle in Las Vegas to compete for the title. The title of the Global Beauty Masters can only go to one team.




Original Air Dates: 02-Dec-2014 to 23-Dec-2014
